{"tid":168224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鐘意自己一個？","createTime":"2017-03-23T11:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T13:28:57.000Z","uid":5190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6fc7f3917dc6ef14d7f5735c85f55d683d940a6","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"唔知點解 人愈大愈唔鐘意多人或者一大棚人去玩呀食呀<br />\n<br />\n每次被迫要去 例如家庭聚會 我都會好撚靜 唔想出聲 同埋好想快啲走<br />\n<br />\n覺得一個人做野可以唔洗驚影響人 又可以做自己鐘意做嘅野 食自己想食嘅野等等<br />\n<br />\n但我成日都驚會比人遺忘 想搞下啲人際關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係唔知自己點諗"},{"pid":"3c1297786721fba7d3abb7cef63e3fbf2be79051","tid":168224,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"唔係特別鐘意，只係慢慢習慣咗"},{"pid":"19250c19dff3c964db62a1be7cb752478047fc93","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係特別鐘意，只係慢慢習慣咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced1f58f210c858a2627e84c5e93bcfcb0fdcdee","tid":168224,"uid":56677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"Reu一個樣，自己另一個樣<br />\n我都鐘意自己靜靜地諗下野"},{"pid":"c908f2f1213eea619402a31a2b65c3673df4ea17","tid":168224,"uid":88433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:51:58.000Z","msg":"我鐘意夜晚自己一個，可以諗下野，遊下車河，唔洗理人點諗，自己鐘意去邊就去邊"},{"pid":"d69036a1c54ca7290868c024618bc32f791eaa5e","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Reu一個樣，自己另一個樣<br />\n我都鐘意自己靜靜地諗下野</blockquote><br />\n我都係 有時有朋友約出街都唔想出 寧願係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日見到啲fd好想出街 無街出嗌生嗌死 有啲諗唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我應該係用唔正常嘅思維去諗 所以諗唔透"},{"pid":"8003de752bdff1a972c88022ec359b97f86de2f3","tid":168224,"uid":21126,"like":0,"dislike":0,