12df27c2e3754f1bc924b8b2471b2a32af","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Reu一個樣，自己另一個樣<br />\n我都鐘意自己靜靜地諗下野</blockquote><br />\n我都係 有時有朋友約出街都唔想出 寧願係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日見到啲fd好想出街 無街出嗌生嗌死 有啲諗唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我應該係用唔正常嘅思維去諗 所以諗唔透</blockquote><br />\n人要社交嘅<br />\n不過一無人陪就嘈之巴閉真係好off</blockquote><br />\n所以都唔係好明佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係多錢 又成日出街"},{"pid":"7e36aeb12f52733c35ea13cefb971377d584e33b","tid":168224,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"咪即係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 : 鍾意自己一個人食飯行山睇戲 但講比朋友知佢地係會恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b128aed5f73cbcb3c45227c7d8201deaa114d8","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪即係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 : 鍾意自己一個人食飯行山睇戲 但講比朋友知佢地係會恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係喎 我會同朋友出街 有正常社交 只係唔多鐘意多人咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7bdea284bec81cd0c6c68b5ae5aa4430ccc2e2","tid":168224,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪即係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 : 鍾意自己一個人食飯行山睇戲 但講比朋友知佢地係會恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過我喺一班人一齊嗰陣會主動帶起話題搞氣氛 所以人際關係都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf1d2644566e033d375c99bc075499f5880644","tid":168224,"uid":52419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪即係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 : 鍾意自己一個人食飯行山睇戲 但講比朋友知佢地係會恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係喎 我會同朋友出街 有正常社交 只係唔多鐘意多人咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你一模一樣呀<br />\n但又成日比人話偽毒<br />\n有時去啲多人嘅活動我都只想靜 <br />\n想快啲番屋企 <br />\n但又怕啲frd odd 所以都會發下膠配合下"},{"pid":"98e96db3110d2a73a3c35dff2fbafb4e9a1ad846","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪即係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 : 鍾意自己一個人食飯行山睇戲 但講比朋友知佢地係會恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過我喺一班人一齊嗰陣會主動帶起話題搞氣氛 所以人際關係都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果真係全部人都同意或者聽你講野 你人際關係都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最憎一大班人一齊個時 講嘅每一句野都要諗過度過<br />\n反而同幾個老死一齊時可以暢所欲言<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27578f4ddacc05ea26c14ec00e39e6200d15448","tid":168224,"uid":29448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"人際關係好好 不過都好鐘意自己一個人既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知自己正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5e1b2ffad6771fb524537b80a482fd84ab7a2c","tid":168224,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"極度鍾意獨處 雖然同人相處完全冇問題<br />\n<br />\n圍威喂好撚煩"},{"pid":"1f81c2ed11ad3a7a4d38386a16e2d6e75efed466","tid":168224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人際關係好好 不過都好鐘意自己一個人既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n