normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己一個出街 啲朋友都唔想約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解對住朋友唔會做到真正既自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人大左就知道中學朋友先係最好<br />\n但係宜家想搵個時間約大家岀黎食飯都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59ce685eec5f355da303ac77dd8bb1f4b5fd8da","tid":168224,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}